urn of the King]]'', ''[[Pirates of the Caribbean: Dead Man's Chest]]'', ''[[The Dark Knight (film)|The Dark Knight]]'', ''[[Harry Potter and the Philosopher's Stone (film)|Harry Potter and the Sorcerer's Stone]]'', ''[[Pirates of the Caribbean: At World's End]]'', ''[[Harry Potter and the Order of the Phoenix (film)|Harry Potter and the Order of the Phoenix]]'', ''[[Harry Potter and the Half-Blood Prince (film)|Harry Potter and the Half-Blood Prince]]'', ''[[The Lord of the Rings: The Two Towers]]'', ''[[Shrek 2]]'', ''[[Harry Potter and the Goblet of Fire (film)|Harry Potter and the Goblet of Fire]]'', ''[[Spider-Man 3]]'', ''[[Ice Age: Dawn of the Dinosaurs]]'', ''[[Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets (film)|Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets]]'', ''[[The Lord of the Rings: The Fellowship of the Ring]]'', ''[[Finding Nemo]]'', ''[[Star Wars: Episode III \u2013 Revenge of the Sith]]'', ''[[Transformers: Revenge of the Fallen]]'', ''[[Harry Potter and the Prisoner of Azkaban (film)|Harry Potter and the Prisoner of Azkaban]]'' and ''[[Shrek the Third]]''.<ref name=\"imdb.com\">[https://www.imdb.com/boxoffice/alltimegross?region=world-wide IMDb.com] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111117141416/http://www.imdb.com/boxoffice/alltimegross?region=world-wide|date=November 17, 2011 }}</ref>\n\n'''The top 15 highest-grossing [[film series]] of the decade are (in order from highest to lowest grossing)'''\n\n[[Harry Potter (film series)|''Harry Potter'' film series]], [[The Lord of the Rings (film series)|''The Lord of the Rings'' film trilogy]], ''[[Pirates of the Caribbean (film series)|Pirates of the Caribbean]]'' film series, ''[[Spider-Man in film|Spider-Man]]'' film series, ''[[Shrek (film series)|Shrek]]'' film series, ''[[Ice Age (franchise)|Ice Age]]'' film series, ''[[Transformers (film series)|Transformers]]'' film series, ''[[X-Men (film series)|X-Men]]'' film series, ''[[Batman in film|Batman]]'' film series' ''[[Batman Begins]]'' and ''[[