am]]\n* [[Kelsey Grammer]]\n* [[Eva Green]]\n* [[Adrian Grenier]]\n* [[Rachel Griffiths]]\n* [[Rupert Grint]]\n* [[Jake Gyllenhaal]]\n* [[Maggie Gyllenhaal]]\n* [[Tony Hale]]\n* [[Michael C. Hall]]\n* [[Jon Hamm]]\n* [[Chelsea Handler]]\n* [[Tom Hanks]]\n* [[Alyson Hannigan]] \n* [[Mariska Hargitay]]\n* [[Mark Harmon]]\n* [[Neil Patrick Harris]]\n* [[Josh Hartnett]]\n* [[Teri Hatcher]]\n* [[Anne Hathaway]]\n* [[Ethan Hawke]]\n* [[Salma Hayek]]\n* [[Sean Hayes]]\n* [[Amber Heard]]\n* [[Patricia Heaton]]\n* [[Katherine Heigl]]\n* [[Marg Helgenberger]]\n* [[Ed Helms]]\n* [[Christina Hendricks]]\n* [[Jill Hennessey]]\n* [[Taraji P. Henson]]\n* [[Cheryl Hines]]\n* [[Philip Seymour Hoffman]]\n* [[Katie Holmes]]\n* [[Terrence Howard]]\n* [[Vanessa Hudgens]]\n* [[Kate Hudson]]\n* [[Felicity Huffman]]\n* [[Ice-T]]\n* [[Michael Imperioli]]\n* [[Hugh Jackman]]\n* [[Joshua Jackson]]\n* [[Samuel L. Jackson]] \n* [[Kevin James]]\n* [[Allison Janney]]\n* [[Scarlett Johansson]]\n* [[Dwayne Johnson]]\n* [[Angelina Jolie]]\n* [[Angus T. Jones]]\n* [[January Jones]]\n* [[Milla Jovovich]]\n* [[Jane Kaczmarek]]\n* [[Mindy Kaling]]\n* [[Vincent Kartheiser]]\n* [[Nicole Kidman]]\n* [[Jimmy Kimmel]]\n* [[Ben Kingsley]]\n* [[Keira Knightley]]\n* [[Jane Krakowski]]\n* [[John Krasinski]]\n* [[Peter Krause]]\n* [[Lisa Kudrow]]\n* [[Mila Kunis]]\n* [[Ashton Kutcher]]\n* [[Shia LaBeouf]]\n* [[Anthony LaPaglia]]\n* [[Hugh Laurie]]\n* [[Taylor Lautner]]\n* [[Jude Law]]\n* [[Martin Lawrence]]\n* [[Denis Leary]]\n* [[Matt LeBlanc]]\n* [[Heath Ledger]]\n* [[Jane Leeves]]\n* [[Jay Leno]]\n* [[Jared Leto]]\n* [[David Letterman]]\n* [[Evangeline Lilly]]\n* [[Blake Lively]]\n* [[Lindsay Lohan]]\n* [[Eva Longoria]]\n* [[Jennifer Lopez]]\n* [[Julia Louis-Dreyfus]]\n* [[Jane Lynch]]\n* [[Bernie Mac]]\n* [[Seth MacFarlane]]\n* [[William H. Macy]]\n* [[Tobey Maguire]]\n* [[Bill Maher]]\n* [[John Mahoney]]\n* [[Jesse L. Martin]]\n* [[Danny Masterson]]\n* [[Rachel McAdams]]\n* [[James McAvoy]]\n* [[Jack McBraye